cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.GR 

The paper involves the use of neural networks for generating sketches based on text descriptions, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the generated sketches are evaluated based on their expressiveness and realism, which falls under graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
